name: [Summer With You] CD ALBUM
description: CAT NO: KT002 The first album by the band was released only on iTunes. The reason was that the band didn’t have a suitable means by which to print them out, now they do. And here it is on it’s one year anniversary, ready to join the “seasonal themed” album collection, of which there will be four. As with all ANWE albums, these songs are still very relevant to the live show and are crucial to own if you have just discovered the band or are intending to enjoy them live at some point. ‘Stephanme’, ‘Slackers Manifesto’ and ‘Lemonade’ are all sing along tracks to the live set. All cases will match the style of the other album ‘spines’ for a complete set. PLEASE NOTE! This album DOES NOT contain lyrics but rather, an introduction inside the booklet about the band and the songs, one by one. To fit each lyric in such a book would require ant-sized fonts (The track ‘Skankalicious’ alone would fill the booklet up!) and so it was decided that the book will contain “insight”. A good read though if you’re into the band. Track listing: 1) Hunter 2) Stay True, Stay You 3) Summer With You 4) Slackers Manifesto 5) Lemonade 6) Skankalicious 7) Stephanme 8) Sing Me Something New 9) Kingstown 10) Enforce The Rhythm 11) I Real Eyes 12) The Why In Sorry

name: [STAY TRUE, STAY YOU] T-SHIRTS. 3 Colours. Only 50 made & numbered.
description: This tshirt is a ‘SERIES ONE’ “Stay True, Stay You” TSHIRT. PLEASE NOTE: LARGE BLUE TSHIRTS ARE NOW SOLD OUT!!!! This shirt won’t be printed again! It’s truly for the fans! Why? “Stay True, Stay You” is the band’s ethos. When we are no longer true, we will no longer be ourselves! Each print is hand numbered by Resheed and the single “Star” represents this as a first edition print. There are 50 of these tshirts, spread across a range of sizes, so the number you get is random. These are almost sold out! Tshirts arrive vacuum sealed symbolising the ultimate freshness!
